snippet.title: Headspace XR | Launch Trailer | Meta Quest Platform
snippet.description:
Headspace XR, exclusive on Meta Quest, invites you to discover a new world made for your mind. 

Headspace XR: a virtual playground where you can move, play, meditate, or just explore on your own or  adventure with your friends — all in breathtaking immersive environments. You’ll feel the real life benefits of mood-boosting games, one-on-one guided meditations with your favorite Headspace teachers, and strengthening your mind-body connection through movement. No matter how you’re feeling, just drop in, take a deep breath, and make time for your best, most mindful self.  

PDP: https://metaque.st/433NJQ9

Developed by Nexus Studios, published by Headspace for Meta Quest.

Handles:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/headspace
